reviewText: kind of odd the way they made the DVD. The Cook tells what he is going to cook (in a accent you cannot understand), and then a gal tells you almost the same spices that are in all the other dishes. It's like all the same dishes, but change the noodles, or something like that. You "get it" but it is not a well made cooking show. The cover looks like quality. I will let you know how the dishes taste later.
